{"id": 1028, "genre": 1001, "title": "【好奇心x兰芝】你都有哪些晚睡强迫症的症状？", "description": "晚睡强迫：当万物沉睡之时你身体不由得迸发出对世间一切无法遏制的好奇心。（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 6131, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160703130055kYUDoZwE64qcRO87.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 3, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-06-07T11:19:39Z", "options": [{"id": 86272, "content": "要刷完所有app才肯睡觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 473931}, {"id": 88066, "content": "睡前一定要上厕所...还要去拉下大门，看看关好没", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 643762}, {"id": 86279, "content": "每天听一会儿音乐，从中感受到了每一个音符都给你带来无尽快乐哦……", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 638460}, {"id": 86280, "content": "和人说完晚安，然后打开好奇心", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 333847}, {"id": 88072, "content": "10点半后每隔半小时焦虑一次但就是不睡", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 643785}, {"id": 86027, "content": "十一点前困成狗，但是又觉得睡觉太早了。过十一点后再也睡不着。", "image": null, "praise_count": 559, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 319909}, {"id": 86283, "content": "人生何必早睡，xx必定长眠。不要浪费时间，乘着清醒刷会儿知乎", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 601840}, {"id": 86028, "content": "喜欢的那个女生总是十一点后想起跟我聊天，想不熬夜也不行了", "image": null, "praise_count": 90, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 107293}, {"id": 86284, "content": "一到床上，就发现手机背面涂了502，简直拿不下来。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 635302}, {"id": 86029, "content": "好像没什么要干的，单纯觉得睡太早是种浪费，然后就磨蹭到一两点", "image": null, "praise_count": 334, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 634358}, {"id": 86285, "content": "聊过天之后，总想点开淘宝，贴吧之类，最后还有消消乐??", "image": "img/option/option/20160702182507Mvi1BSLyR5spwq90", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 637514}, {"id": 88077, "content": "理由有太多，总结一下就是手机(ಥ_ಥ)", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 627264}, {"id": 86030, "content": "晚上10点，手机还有10%就充满电了，嗯，充电充一夜不好，等充满了再睡吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 163, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 446026}, {"id": 86286, "content": "睡前一定一定一定要上厕所……就算没有货", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 541393}, {"id": 86031, "content": "早睡总觉得浪费了大好时光，用来看电视玩游戏的大好时光！", "image": null, "praise_count": 76, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 44}, {"id": 86287, "content": "偶尔看到了一部好看的电视剧，一定要看完才睡！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 614299}, {"id": 86288, "content": "和好多朋友说晚安…然后开始看iPad", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 637463}, {"id": 86033, "content": "带耳塞戴眼罩，不困成狗不睡觉！", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 630637}, {"id": 86289, "content": "十二点之前没睡着 那就完了 意味着一整晚都睡不着了", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 638574}, {"id": 86034, "content": "手机开音乐定时 喜欢的人不说晚安就睡不着 手机必须放在枕头边能闭着眼睛摸到的地方", "image": "img/option/option/20160702182819zi913eQmojUYKVvS.jpg", "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 637652}, {"id": 86290, "content": "一定要让男票发晚安短信！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 597196}, {"id": 86035, "content": "就算11点躺在床上也要再玩2个多小时的手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 237, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 632333}, {"id": 86291, "content": "追剧不追完睡不着", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 436675}, {"id": 86292, "content": "希望保持双手干净，买了免洗洗手液，40-60mins涂一次。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 311434}, {"id": 86037, "content": "他怎么还不回复我是出去野了么！（生气", "image": null, "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 181495}, {"id": 86293, "content": "突然发现自己看错题目了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 311434}, {"id": 86038, "content": "非得等到那个人对我说晚安，不然会一直在半梦半醒状态下在脑子中", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 637255}, {"id": 94230, "content": "不困", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 663214}, {"id": 86039, "content": "早起做事情太困难了！还是晚睡会吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 40, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 632333}, {"id": 86295, "content": "每晚下自习困到不行 但只要去跑步 回来跟打鸡血一样", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 583955}, {"id": 86040, "content": "内心的空虚寂寞无力感", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1016624}, {"id": 86296, "content": "睡觉绝望", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 637716}, {"id": 86041, "content": "一定要听两集\"黄河鬼事\"才能睡踏实", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 488918}, {"id": 86042, "content": "有事情没完成，绝对睡不着", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 555974}, {"id": 90907, "content": "打开微博一刷就两个小时没有了……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 651629}, {"id": 86044, "content": "不看奇葩说，不可睡眠去", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 555995}, {"id": 86045, "content": "脑子里说再不睡对身体不好，但眼睛没闭上，手指滑动没停过(-᷅_-᷄)", "image": null, "praise_count": 45, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 511538}, {"id": 86046, "content": "电视剧，综艺，游戏，小说，太多东西想睇，都唔想训。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 581353}, {"id": 86051, "content": "“再看一下就睡...” 于是再也没有困意，直至筋疲力尽，累了才沉沉进入梦乡", "image": null, "praise_count": 96, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 419410}, {"id": 86052, "content": "晚上不想睡，白天不想起", "image": null, "praise_count": 47, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 206007}, {"id": 86055, "content": "一直睡不着，总是有想不完的东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 618432}, {"id": 86056, "content": "睡觉前觉得要看视频放松一下，然后就没有然后了", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 600837}, {"id": 86057, "content": "手机刷屏强迫症", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 637691}, {"id": 86058, "content": "睡太早感觉浪费生命～", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 589115}, {"id": 86315, "content": "说好的早睡早起呢 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 139970}, {"id": 86060, "content": "本想听歌催眠结果\n听歌听到流泪感慨情绪万千\n想起以前的自己\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 525339}, {"id": 86061, "content": "总觉得晚上可以做更多的事干嘛要等明天呢，结果就是每天都睡不着了", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 637405}, {"id": 86063, "content": "这个没看，那个还没看，嗯嗯，看一会儿就睡。诶，前任XXX貌似有了新恋情，点开她的微博翻翻翻，@的这个人貌似是她男友，再点开她男友的微博翻翻翻…", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 623793}, {"id": 86064, "content": "所有有意思的视频帖子在准备关上手机睡觉的时候一股脑儿蹦了出来", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 611939}, {"id": 87857, "content": "说好12点，最后不知道怎么天就亮了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 643043}]}